Processes:
Delay in minutes after which a running process that hasn't been updated is automatically cancelled.

This parameter is useful if a crash occurs during a process runtime and blocks other processes execution.
Leave blank to ignore.

Ce paramètre est utile quand un processus se plante et bloque l'exécution des autres processus.
